[{"_path":"/legacy-articles/2021-07-27-windows-shortcut-setting-guide-with-macos-style","_dir":"legacy-articles","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"en","_empty":false,"title":"macOS 風格的 Windows 鍵盤按鍵設定指南","description":"","excerpt":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"前言"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"前言"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"最近因為 Macbook Pro 送修，恰逢一個需要另一台電腦的空窗期，所以就買了一台迷你主機並且安裝 Windows，打算作為備援以及娛樂、遊戲機 (君不見我的 Steam 遊戲中一堆都是 Windows only TAT)。而從 macOS 切換到 Windows 時，最難以上手的應該就是鍵盤與按鍵的使用。我是一個以 macOS 習慣為主的使用者，所以自然是去思考怎麼讓 Windows 上的按鍵與 macOS 盡量保持一致囉！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"為了修改按鍵的配置，我們會需要使用 Microsoft 自行推出的好用工具 — PowerToys，此軟體除了修改按鍵對應外，還有擁有許多好用的功能，我們先不再這邊展開。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"到 PowerToys 的 GitHub 去下載最新的版本並且安裝："},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/microsoft/PowerToys/releases","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"https://github.com/microsoft/PowerToys/releases"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"打開 PowerToys 並且來到鍵盤管理器，就可以去重新對應單個按鍵與組合鍵。以下提到的 Ctrl, Alt, Shift，統一是指改左邊的，在有覆蓋到真正需要的快捷鍵時，還有右邊的組合鍵可以使用。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"一般按鍵配置"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"一般按鍵配置"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"單按鍵"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"單按鍵"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"將「Caps Lock」對應為「Escape 」(在 macOS 因為沒有實體鍵盤的關係，已經習慣這樣使用)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"將「Alt」對應為「Ctrl」以切換視窗，以達到像 macOS 使用 command 鍵的手感"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"del","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text",